House: townhouse, farmhouse
City: new-york, rome
2 different pets are kept: hamster, pony
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, skateboard
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the fan of blues is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the townhouse house is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Beverage      | 7up          | milk       |
| Music-Genre          | punk   | blues   |
| House           | farmhouse   | townhouse     |
| City   | new-york | rome        |
| Pet           | hamster      | pony       |
| Sport         | rowing       | water-polo |
| Transport     | bus          | skateboard |

